creator: Alice Meynell
description:
LibriVox recording of Poems by Alice Meynell.
Read in English by Sonia; Ryan Fry; Daniel Hennis; Lucy Kempton; Just Leah; Amber Jewels; Anusha Iyer; Daphne Lin; Fairchay; Newgatenovelist
This is a volume of poems by Alice Meynell. - Summary by Carolin
For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording.

For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org.
